title: V08 — Light & Dark
story: familyzoo
author: Sharpee Tutorial
description: Verify dark nocturnal exhibit and flashlight illumination

---

# V8 teaches: isDark rooms, LightSourceTrait, SwitchableTrait

# Get the keycard and unlock the staff gate
> take keycard
[OK: contains "Taken"]

> south
[OK: contains "Main Path"]

> unlock gate with keycard
[OK: contains "unlock"]

> open gate
[OK: contains "open"]

> south
[OK: contains "Supply Room"]

# Take the flashlight
> take flashlight
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Go to the nocturnal exhibit (dark!)
> south
[OK: contains "dark"]

# Can't see anything
> look
[OK: contains "dark"]

# Go back and switch on the flashlight
> north
[OK: contains "Supply Room"]

> switch on flashlight
[OK: contains "on"]

# Now re-enter the nocturnal exhibit
> south
[OK: contains "Nocturnal Animals"]

# With the flashlight on, we can see the animals!
> look
[OK: contains "sugar gliders"]

> examine owl
[OK: contains "barn owl"]
[OK: contains "heart-shaped"]

> examine galagos
[OK: contains "large round eyes"]

# Go back out
> north
[OK: contains "Supply Room"]
